QuestData.Title: Corruption Manifest
QuestData.Description:
The corruption of the Old Gods is often so foul it manifests itself in physical form.
We have seen this with the Sha. This time is no different.
Cull this corruption wherever you see it spread. It must not be left to flourish.
QuestData.LogDescription: Kill $1oa Putrid Ichors in Vale of Eternal Blossoms.
